name: AbstracTz #1 - Magnificient Illusion
description:
AbstracTz - a new NFT collection on Tezos
Each AbsracTz created is unique and designed by me moonboi.
There will be 100 artworks in total, which will be released periodically. If you like my art style and want to support a fellow drawer, feel free to bid on my auctions.

The Magnificient Illusion
As you stare into the picture, you'll slowly recognize the variety of colors, the hidden patterns and feel the illusion.
